{
  "name": "RPlog_The_Lost_and_Found",
  "title": "The Lost and Found",
  "summary": "On the desert world of Palanhi, Jessalyn Valios, Lando Calrissian, and the exhausted young Shenner search the city's small medical center for the missing Paul Nighman, who had vanished after suffering severe internal bleeding. They find him recovering in a bacta-treated, restrained \"John Doe,\" tended by the flirtatious Dr. Tantra, who trades banter with the charming Lando. A tearful Shenner, who searched all night fearing Paul dead, collapses into sleep in his arms once reunited, and Paul carries her back to the ship Black Dragon and tucks her in. Afterward, Paul takes a moonlit walk with the troubled Jessalyn through the starport district, where she confides her painful, conflicted love for Luke Skywalker. Paul gently counsels patience and offers to stay behind to watch over Luke for her, and she tearfully begs him to bring Luke back safely. The two part with warmth and tenderness, Paul kissing her forehead before she retires to sleep.",
